<DocsLayout title="Guides" description="Step-by-step guides for DAO Launcher Kit">
  <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Guides</h1>
    
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
      Step-by-step tutorials and guides to help you master DAO Launcher Kit.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose">
      <!-- Creating a DAO -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/10 to-blue-500/10 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Creating a DAO</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Learn how to launch and initialize a new DAO on the Internet Computer.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">What you'll learn:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Setting up DAO configuration (name, token, governance)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Initializing the DAO through the dashboard</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Inviting initial members and assigning roles</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span>Testing your DAO with sample proposals</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-950 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
          <h4 class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Quick Steps:</h4>
          <ol class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1 list-decimal list-inside">
            <li>Navigate to "Launch DAO" in the main app</li>
            <li>Fill in DAO details (name, description, token info)</li>
            <li>Configure governance parameters</li>
            <li>Click "Launch DAO" and wait for confirmation</li>
            <li>Initialize DAO from your dashboard</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <a 
          href="https://7e7p4-jyaaa-aaaao-a4pba-cai.icp0.io/launch"
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-cyan-500 rounded-lg text-white font-semibold hover:bg-cyan-600 transition-colors"
        >
          Try It Now
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Governance -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/10 to-emerald-500/10 border border-green-500/30 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-green-500/50 transition-all">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Governance & Voting</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Create proposals, vote on decisions, and execute approved actions.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Proposal Types:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Tokenomics:</strong> Change rewards, fees, supply</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Governance:</strong> Update voting rules, quorum</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Treasury:</strong> Fund allocation, spending</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>General:</strong> Community decisions</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-950 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
          <h4 class="text-green-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Voting Process:</h4>
          <ol class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1 list-decimal list-inside">
            <li>Create proposal with title and description</li>
            <li>Members vote (Yes/No/Abstain)</li>
            <li>Voting power based on staked tokens</li>
            <li>Proposal passes if quorum + majority reached</li>
            <li>Approved proposals execute automatically</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="text-cyan-400 text-sm">
          ‚ÑπÔ∏è Voting power = Staked tokens √ó Time-weighted multiplier
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Staking -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/10 to-pink-500/10 border border-purple-500/30 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all opacity-60">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Staking & Rewards</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Lock tokens to earn rewards and gain voting power in your DAO.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Benefits:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Earn Rewards:</strong> Proportional to stake amount</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Voting Power:</strong> More stake = more influence</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Auto-Compounding:</strong> Rewards automatically restaked</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Time Multiplier:</strong> Longer stakes = higher rewards</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-950 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
          <h4 class="text-yellow-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">How to Stake:</h4>
          <pre class="text-gray-300 text-xs"><code>1. Go to DAO Dashboard ‚Üí Staking
2. Enter amount to stake
3. Choose lock duration (optional)
4. Confirm transaction
5. Start earning rewards immediately</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/30 rounded p-3">
          <p class="text-yellow-300 text-sm mb-0">
            ‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Note:</strong> Unstaking may have a cooldown period. Check your DAO's staking rules.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Treasury Management -->
      <div class="bg-gray-900 border border-cyan-500/30 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-cyan-500 transition-colors">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üí∞</div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-3">Treasury Management</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          Manage DAO funds with multi-signature security and transparent operations.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Features:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Multi-sig Security:</strong> Requires multiple approvals</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Deposits:</strong> Accept ICP and ICRC1 tokens</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Withdrawals:</strong> Controlled by governance proposals</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-red-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
              <span><strong>Audit Trail:</strong> Complete transaction history</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-950 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
          <h4 class="text-red-400 text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Common Operations:</h4>
          <ul class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Deposit:</strong> Add funds to treasury</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Withdraw:</strong> Send funds (requires proposal)</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>View Balance:</strong> Check current holdings</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Transaction History:</strong> Audit all operations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="text-cyan-400 text-sm">
          üîí All treasury operations require governance approval for security
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/10 to-blue-500/10 border border-cyan-500/20 rounded-xl p-8 not-prose">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Need Help?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
        Join our community for support and discussions.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
        <a 
